{"tid":1940392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[0114] 2名連儂手足凌晨於粉嶺站被大批警員拘捕","createTime":"2020-03-23T17:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T17:18:30.000Z","uid":231583,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"bec312e323f9c8de8757592f80fc5ed7abb21145","tid":1940392,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T17:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/27Rwx4v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F27Rwx4v.jpg&h=9e2990f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n0114 #反修例抗爭 #粉嶺 #連儂牆 #便衣警員 #被捕人士<br />\n粉嶺有2名張貼「連儂牆」的青年被捕。凌晨近1時，在港鐵站外天橋，有2名青年張貼反修例標語，2名便衣警員現身，制服2人，拘捕並帶走。軍裝警員增援，在現場拉起封鎖線調查。<br />\n#商台<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/realtimenewsbroadcasts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frealtimenewsbroadcasts&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1vRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=e923ba25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/realtimenewsbroadcasts</a>"},{"pid":"76145682e9aa59d880f4c035457d497cc84f864a","tid":1940392,"uid":256181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T17:47:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4de6e96ba9f6907558e6b3fc61f872613f85df2c","tid":1940392,"uid":231583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T17:48:01.000Z","msg":"幫手推，流動文宣已經大把人做緊，唔好再要更多手足被濫捕黎提醒我地既每日任務啦好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n[多圖] 其實連儂手足玩開花真係好撚癲 根本無得拆<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1919485\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1919485</a><br />\n<br />\n可以share去以下group振軍心，日日都大把人做緊，隨時隨地貼幾張文宣真係咁難做到？<br />\n<br />\n香港人的連儂牆<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/906808683014535/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F906808683014535%2F&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1vRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=91ca3c89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/906808683014535/</a><br />\n<br />\n18區連儂 消息頻道<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Lennonovazed_channel\" data-sr-url=\"